headline: Amy Friedrich to Speak at 2025 UBS Financial Services Conference
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, January 16, 2025--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) announced today that Amy Friedrich, president, Benefits & Protection, will participate in a fireside chat at the UBS Financial Services Conference on Monday, February 10, 2025, beginning at approximately 11:20 a.m. Eastern Time. Friedrich will participate in a question-and-answer session covering a variety of industry and company topics.
